48
00:03:34,010 --> 00:03:36,110
So let's go back and wait for her.

49
00:03:47,020 --> 00:03:48,190
She came earlier than expected.

50
00:03:51,740 --> 00:03:52,940
I got a valuable thing by chance.

51
00:03:53,480 --> 00:03:55,650
