00:31:21,700 --> 00:31:23,140
All the gold bricks are here.

631
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:25,550
You put all the gold bricks in the wall.

632
00:31:26,010 --> 00:31:27,000
We hid gold bricks

633
00:31:27,590 --> 00:31:28,920
